ervice Inspector for New\\nSouth Wales), Duncan (representing the Com\\nmonwialth Public Service), C. W. Kelety\\n(manager) and T. Garratt (director) of the\\nCivil Service Stores, and F. A. Coghlan (for-\\nmerly Auditor-General).\", \"line_offsets\": [[0, 19], [20, 30], [31, 69], [70, 109], [110, 151], [152, 194], [195, 237], [238, 276], [277, 312], [313, 350], [351, 391], [392, 433], [434, 472], [473, 514], [515, 556], [557, 599], [600, 640], [641, 683], [684, 722], [723, 762], [763, 808], [809, 851], [852, 892], [893, 932], [933, 943], [944, 989], [990, 1034], [1035, 1076], [1077, 1119], [1120, 1161], [1162, 1207], [1208, 1251], [1252, 1292], [1293, 1325], [1326, 1366], [1367, 1405], [1406, 1446], [1447, 1488], [1489, 1523], [1524, 1566], [1567, 1610], [1611, 1654], [1655, 1696], [1697, 1738], [1739, 1783], [1784, 1826], [1827, 1867], [1868, 1910], [1911, 1953], [1954, 1993], [1994, 2036], [2037, 2082], [2083, 2106]], \"sentence_offsets\": [[0, 13], [14, 30], [31, 350], [351, 387], [388, 545], [546, 741], [742, 868], [869, 943], [944, 949], [950, 1062], [1063, 1145], [1146, 1235], [1236, 1325], [1326, 1372], [1373, 1523], [1524, 1600], [1601, 1670], [1671, 1811], [1812, 2106]], \"num_tokens\": 306, \"num_chars\": 2106, \"quality_report\": {\"ocr_quality_score\": 0.93, \"cer\": 0.032319, \"wer\": 0.186885, \"nb_char_substitutions\": 60, \"nb_char_deletions\": 3, \"nb_char_insertions\": 5}}, \"ocr_postcorrection_output\": {\"transcription_unit\": \"None\", \"ocr_postcorrection_system\": \"None\", \"num_tokens\": -1, \"num_chars\": -1, \"quality_report\": {\"ocr_quality_score\": -1, \"cer\": -1, \"wer\": -1, \"nb_char_substitutions\": -1, \"nb_char_deletions\": -1, \"nb_char_insertions\": -1}}}","{\"document_metadata\": {\"document_id\": \"16705000\", \"primary_dataset_name\": \"overproof-combined\", \"primary_dataset_filename\": \"data/03_curated/overproof/dataset2/rawTextAndHumanCorrectionAndOverproofCorrectionTriples/allArticles.corrected.txt\", \"primary_dataset