 remain in a constant\\nstate of bankruptcy and the pooplo\\nwill be iu tho Concommo which Mr\\nJones desires to skim\", \"line_offsets\": [[0, 12], [13, 40], [41, 73], [74, 105], [106, 136], [137, 154], [155, 186], [187, 217], [218, 246], [247, 275], [276, 304], [305, 337], [338, 369], [370, 397], [398, 430], [431, 464], [465, 502], [503, 536], [537, 568], [569, 600], [601, 633], [634, 661], [662, 695], [696, 729], [730, 763], [764, 797], [798, 833], [834, 866], [867, 897], [898, 922], [923, 955], [956, 986], [987, 1017], [1018, 1051], [1052, 1085], [1086, 1115], [1116, 1145], [1146, 1178], [1179, 1212], [1213, 1248], [1249, 1283], [1284, 1318], [1319, 1351], [1352, 1382], [1383, 1418], [1419, 1452], [1453, 1489], [1490, 1501], [1502, 1530], [1531, 1566], [1567, 1603], [1604, 1638], [1639, 1668], [1669, 1700], [1701, 1733], [1734, 1763], [1764, 1797], [1798, 1827], [1828, 1862], [1863, 1897], [1898, 1930], [1931, 1961], [1962, 1993], [1994, 2028], [2029, 2061], [2062, 2094], [2095, 2126], [2127, 2160], [2161, 2196], [2197, 2227], [2228, 2260], [2261, 2294], [2295, 2329], [2330, 2361], [2362, 2396], [2397, 2429], [2430, 2465], [2466, 2498], [2499, 2532], [2533, 2562], [2563, 2594], [2595, 2626], [2627, 2662], [2663, 2694], [2695, 2724], [2725, 2758], [2759, 2790], [2791, 2827], [2828, 2863], [2864, 2891], [2892, 2907], [2908, 2941], [2942, 2976], [2977, 3007], [3008, 3044], [3045, 3075], [3076, 3107], [3108, 3141], [3142, 3175], [3176, 3207], [3208, 3239], [3240, 3258], [3259, 3293], [3294, 3329], [3330, 3367], [3368, 3400], [3401, 3435], [3436, 3465], [3466, 3500], [3501, 3537], [3538, 3570], [3571, 3602], [3603, 3636], [3637, 3671], [3672, 3704], [3705, 3726]], \"sentence_offsets\": [[0, 12], [13, 33], [34, 141], [142, 154], [155, 297], [298, 397], [398, 403], [404, 557], [558, 649], [650, 767], [768, 922], [923, 1145], [1146, 1189], [1190, 1501], [1502, 1556], [1557, 1650], [1651, 1733], [1734, 1827], [1828, 1916], [1917, 1983], [1984, 2077], [2078, 2313], [2314,